#	User Stories										
1	As a customer, I want to login securely										
2	As a seller, I want to login Securely										
3	As an admin, Iwant to login Securely										
4	As a customer, I should have the ability to logout of my account										
5	As a seller, I should have the ability to logout of my account										
6	As an admin, I should have the ability to logout of my account										
7	As a customer, I want to register an account to browse the items i want										
8	As a seller, I want to register an account to be able to sell										
9	As a customer, I want to update my profile										
10	As a seller, I want to update my businesss profile										
11	As a customer, i want the ability to delete my account										
12	As a seller, I want the ability to delete my account										
13	As a customer, I want to browse items currently selling										
14	As a customer, I want to add item/s to cart										
15	As a customer, I want to add item/s to wishlist										
16	As a customer, I want to make orders										
17	As a customer, I want to know if my order is approved										
18	As a customer, i want the ability to remove items from my cart										
19	As a customer, I want the ability to remove items from my wishlist										
20	As a customer, i want to set how many items i want to order in my cart										
21	As a customer, I want the ability to report items when it is sus										
22	As a customer, I want the ability to report businesses when it is sus										
23	As a customer, I want the ability to leave reviews on an item										
24	As a customer, I want the ability to leave reviews on a business										
25	As a customer, I want the ability to see the details of an item if i want to										
26	As a customer, i want the ability to directly order itmes without going to cart										
27	As a seller, I want the ability to create items to sell										
28	As a seller, I want the ability to sell items										
29	As a seller, I want to see the items that im selling										
30	As a seller, i want the ability to delete the items im selling										
31	As a seller I want the ability to update items im selling										
32	As a seller, I want the ability to browse the orders in my items										
33	As a seller, I want the ability to check if my item is delivered										
34	As a customer, I want to filter items based on category when visiting business page										
35	As a customer, I want to visit the business page if i want to										
36	As a customer, I want to filter items currently selling (New and Top Rated)										
37	As a seller, I want to add cetgory on the items im selling										
38	As a seller, I want a report to know what items is the top seller										
39	As a seller, i want to create coupon codes on certain items										
40	As a seller, I want the ability to remove categories on items im selling										
41	As a seller, I want the ability to create category types										
42	As a seller, I want the ability to remove categories on items im selling										
43	As a seller, I want the ability to add categories										
44	As a seller, I want the ability to update category names										
45	As a seller, I want the ability to add my own logo to show it to my customers when they visit my page										
46	As a customer, I want the ability to apply coupon code on items										
47	As a seller, I want the ability to comment on the reviews on my items										
48	As a seller, i want the ability to comment on the reviews on my business										
49	As an admin, I want the ability to approve businesses first before they can proceed to making items, etc on their business										
50	As an admin, I want the ability to manage user accounts										
51	As an admin, i want the ability to see reported items										
52	As an admin, i want the ability to remove reported items										
53	As an admin, i want the ability to manage user accounts										
54	As an admin, I want the ability to manage business accounts										
55	As an admin, i want the ability to delete user accounts										
56	As an admin, I want the ability to delete business accounts										
57	As the business owner of quickbuy, I want the customers to browse the items on my shop even when dont have any account										
58	As the business owner of quickbuy, I want to prompt my potential customers to login or register when they want to add to cart/wishlist the items if they dont have an account yet										
59	As the business owner of quickybuy, I want a landing page on my page										
60	As an admin, I want the ability to create other admin accounts with lesser permissions (no ability to create other admin)										